### SMS Portal API Testing

# Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
@accessToken = your-jwt-access-token-here

### 1. User Registration
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "testpassword123",
  "password_confirm": "testpassword123",
  "phone_number": "+1234567890",
  "company": "Test Company"
}

### 2. User Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "testpassword123"
}

### 3. Get User Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4. Send SMS
POST {{baseUrl}}/send-sms/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message_text": "Hello! This is a test SMS from SMS Portal.",
  "recipients": ["+1234567890", "+0987654321"],
  "sender_id": null,
  "template_id": null
}

### 5. Get SMS History
GET {{baseUrl}}/history/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 6. Get SMS History with Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/history/?status=sent&start_date=2024-01-01&end_date=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 7. Get Dashboard Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 8. Get Templates
GET {{baseUrl}}/templates/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 9. Create Template
POST {{baseUrl}}/templates/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Welcome Message",
  "content": "Welcome to our service! Your account has been successfully created.",
  "is_active": true
}

### 10. Get Sender IDs
GET {{baseUrl}}/senders/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 11. Create Sender ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/senders/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "COMPANY",
  "description": "Company branded sender ID",
  "is_active": true
}

### 12. Get API Credentials
GET {{baseUrl}}/credentials/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 13. Update API Credentials
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/credentials/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "api_key": "your-mysmsmantra-api-key",
  "client_id": "your-client-id",
  "sender_id": "your-sender-id",
  "is_active": true
}

### 14. Bulk SMS Send
POST {{baseUrl}}/bulk-send/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message_text": "Bulk SMS test message",
  "recipients": ["+1111111111", "+2222222222", "+3333333333"],
  "sender_id": null
}

### 15. Token Refresh
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/token/refresh/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refresh": "your-refresh-token-here"
}

### Test MySMSMantra API directly (for debugging)
GET https://api.mylogin.co.in/api/v2/SendSMS?ApiKey=YOUR_API_KEY&ClientId=YOUR_CLIENT_ID&SenderId=YOUR_SENDER_ID&Message=Test%20message&MobileNumbers=1234567890&Is_Unicode=0&Is_Flash=0